blisher=BFI|accessdate=22 April 2013}}</ref> * ''Battery Casting on Site'' (1966) - photography.<ref>{{cite web|title=Battery Casting on Site|url=http://ftvdb.bfi.org.uk/sift/title/77410|work=BFI Film & TV Database|publisher=BFI|accessdate=22 April 2013}}</ref> * ''Fire Test on Structural Concrete Beams'' (1967) - photography.<ref>{{cite web|title=Fire Test on Structural Concrete Beams|url=http://ftvdb.bfi.org.uk/sift/title/81436|work=BFI Film & TV Database|publisher=BFI|accessdate=22 April 2013}}</ref> * ''To be continued&nbsp;...'' (1990), - contributor (third programme in series ''comics - the ninth art.'').<ref>{{cite web|title=To be continued&nbsp;... |url=http://www.worldcat.org/title/to-be-continued/oclc/81223466&referer=brief_results|work=OCLC WorldCat|accessdate=16 June 2014}}</ref>
